## The Most Important Habit

Every day, pick **one method** from any controller. Read it. Then close the file and try to write it from memory. You don't need to be perfect — the act of trying and failing and checking is what builds understanding.

After 30 days of this, you will understand this codebase better than most people who worked on it.
